  "prompt": "How do I recover my Gmail password with a recovery mobile number and a Gmail address?",
  "response": "To recover your Gmail password using your recovery mobile number and your Gmail address, you can follow these steps:\n\n1. **Go to the Google Account Recovery Page**:\n   - Open your web browser and go to the [Google Account Recovery page](https://accounts.google.com/signin/recovery).\n\n2. **Enter Your Email Address**:\n   - Type in your Gmail address and click \u201cNext\u201d.\n\n3. **Click on \"Forgot password?\"**:\n   - When prompted to enter your password, click on the \"Forgot password?\" link.\n\n4. **Choose Recovery Options**:\n   - Google will provide several recovery options. If you have set up your recovery mobile number, you should see an option to receive a verification code via SMS.\n   - Select the option that mentions your recovery mobile number and click \u201cSend\u201d.\n\n5. **Receive the Verification Code**:\n   - Check your mobile device for a text message from Google containing the verification code.\n\n6. **Enter the Verification Code**:\n   - Input the verification code you received in the designated field on the recovery page and click \u201cNext\u201d.\n\n7. **Create a New Password**:\n   - After verifying your identity, you should be prompted to create a new password. Make sure to choose a strong password that you haven\u2019t used before.\n\n8. **Finish**:\n   - Once you\u2019ve set your new password, you can access your Gmail account. Consider updating your account recovery options to ensure you can recover your account more easily in the future.\n\n### Tips:\n- Make sure your recovery mobile number is currently active and can receive texts.\n- If you don\u2019t have access to your recovery mobile number or if there are issues with the recovery process, you can try answering security questions or look for other recovery options provided by Google.\n- It's a good practice to enable two-step verification for added security once you regain access to your account.\n\nIf you encounter any issues during the process, refer to Google\u2019s help resources for additional assistance.",
